{"tid":484113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最近睇完個深海po 好想食","createTime":"2017-11-29T19:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T19:35:41.000Z","uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a95fb5dfb6630aa17033505cedccd92ed11341eb","tid":484113,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:18:14.000Z","msg":"講真 由細到大都好鍾意食啲奇撚怪怪嘅野<br />\n只要唔違反自己嘅 都會想試下食<br />\n利申: 冇食過貓狗兔<br />\n最特別都係食嗰啲炸昆蟲 同蚯蚓咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完個深海po 認真好想試下咩味<br />\n有冇巴打食過分享下<br />\n或者畀個地步黎 畀細佬我親身去食都好<br />\n甚至組團食都冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪應該開係飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過求撚其啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcef8ca3bad1458f799c65642740a10f9d338f9b","tid":484113,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}